The doc subdirectory has three files:

1. sysadmin.ps - contains the acknowledgment section and describes the 
steps you are supposed to follow if you want to use the tool.

2. manual.ps - the discourse tagging manual that we developed and use.

3. tagging.ps - the paper below.


@InProceedings{marcu-tagging99,
  author = 	 {Daniel Marcu and Estibaliz Amorrort and Magdalena Romera},
  title = 	 {Experiments in Constructing a Corpus of Discourse Trees},
  booktitle = 	 {Proceedings of the ACL'99 Workshop on Standards and Tools for Discourse Tagging},
  pages =	 { },
  year =	 1999,
  address =	 {University of Maryland},
  month =	 {June 22}
}


Please send any comments and suggestions to marcu@isi.edu.